# Assets Insurance Prospective Recoveries Reinsurance Outstanding Claims Provision Gross Amount

## identifier
de8963

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of reinsurance recoverables, being amounts due to the reporting party under a reinsurance arrangement that arise from the recognition of Outstanding Claims Liabilities in accordance with relevant reporting standards.  The value must be reported net of any provisions for doubtful debts.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Insurance.Prospective.RecoveriesReinsuranceOutstandingClaimsProvisionGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.05
- period=instant
